==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-uk-unununium.ogg|Audio (UK)}}
===Etymology===
Systematic name, literally "element 111" from [[un-]] "one" (Latin [[unus]]) + un- + un- + [[-ium]] which forms names of elements.  

===Noun===
'''unununium''' ''(symbol:'' '''[[Uuu]]''')
# ''(systematic name, now historical)'' [[roentgenium]].

